<paragraph blockId="36.[151,1437,153,1971]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1907,1934]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Comments:</emphasis>
Rare species that appears to be endemic to northeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[969,1040,1907,1933]" name="Brazil" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, although it is known from two different ecoregions there—the Atlantic rainforest and the Caatinga.
</paragraph>
